"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Secure data storage"}]]}],["$","li","42",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Access control per user role"}]]}],["$","li","43",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Encrypted communications"}]]}],["$","h2","44",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"Real Example: A Physio Clinic in South Bombay"}],["$","p","45",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"We built a CRM for a physiotherapy clinic that was managing patients via WhatsApp and Excel."}]]}],["$","p","46",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Before:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":""}]]}],["$","li","47",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"5 hours/day on patient management (scheduling, follow-ups, payment tracking)"}]]}],["$","li","48",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"30% no-show rate (lost revenue)"}]]}],["$","li","49",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Cannot see treatment progress across patients"}]]}],["$","li","50",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Insurance claims take 2 weeks to process"}]]}],["$","p","51",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"After custom CRM:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":""}]]}],["$","li","52",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"30 minutes/day on patient management (mostly automated)"}]]}],["$","li","53",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"No-show rate dropped to 12%"}]]}],["$","li","54",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Treatment completion tracking shows which therapies work best"}]]}],["$","li","55",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Insurance claims processed in 2 days"}]]}],["$","p","56",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Build cost:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" $15,000\n"}],["$","strong","3",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Payback period:"}],["$","span","4",{"children":" 2-3 months"}]]}],["$","h2","57",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"How to Build Healthcare CRM Right"}],["$","h3","58",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"Start with paper"}],["$","p","59",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Do not jump to digital immediately. Spend a week with your clinic staff and understand their actual paper workflow. Digitizing a good process is easy. Digitizing a messy process just creates a messy digital system."}]]}],["$","h3","60",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"Model around providers"}],["$","p","61",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Unlike sales CRMs that model around leads and deals, build your data model around providers, patients, and appointments. Everything else flows from these three things."}]]}],["$","h3","62",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"Integrate with existing systems"}],["$","p","63",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"If the clinic uses a specific billing system or appointment software, the custom CRM needs to integrate with it. Data moving between systems without manual entry is the goal."}]]}],["$","h3","64",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"Build for your specific constraints"}],["$","p","65",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"A dental clinic has different workflows than a physiotherapy clinic, which has different workflows than a diagnostic center. The CRM should be customized to your specific workflows, not a generic \"healthcare\" template."}]]}],["$","h3","66",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"Get provider buy-in early"}],["$","p","67",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"The success of a clinic CRM depends entirely on whether providers and staff actually use it. Involve them in the requirements gathering and early testing."}]]}],["$","h2","68",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"Cost Breakdown"}],["$","p","69",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"For a typical clinic with 2-3 providers:"}]]}],["$","li","70",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Basic CRM:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" $8,000 to $12,000"}]]}],["$","li","71",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"With billing integration:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Add $3,000 to $5,000"}]]}],["$","li","72",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"With appointment reminders:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Add $2,000 to $3,000"}]]}],["$","li","73",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"With WhatsApp integration:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Add $1,000 to $2,000"}]]}],["$","p","74",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Total: $14,000 to $22,000 for a fully functional healthcare CRM."}]]}],["$","p","75",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Compare that to Salesforce ($300/user/month) or HubSpot ($50-3200/month) which will never actually work for healthcare, and the custom CRM becomes obviously the better choice."}]]}],["$","h2","76",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"The Bottom Line"}],["$","p","77",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Healthcare is too specialized for generic CRMs. Clinics that build custom systems do not just operate more efficiently. They provide better patient care because all the information is